※Regarding battles, this game has four attack attributes: \I[77]
physical, \I[70] holy, \I[71] dark, and \I[84] mucous membrane
contact. The enemies in the lewd realm are weak against \I[70] holy
attribute, have strong resistance against \I[71] dark attribute, and
also have some resistance against \I[77] physical attribute.

In the initial state, Araka's attack skills are composed of \I[77]
physical and \I[70] holy attributes, so it is easier to deal damage to
the lewd realm's spirits and demons. However... please be aware that
as Araka's corruption progresses, her skills may also transform into
\I[71] dark attributes.

※Regarding Araka's resistance, Araka is weak against \I[84] mucous
membrane contact attribute. If Araka is in good condition, the enemies
cannot use \I[84] mucous membrane contact attribute attacks.

However, if Araka falls, gets restrained, or reaches climax and
becomes weak, the enemies will immediately launch \I[84] mucous
membrane contact attacks.

When using the \I[72] icon buff skill, Araka temporarily gains
resistance to knockdown and restraint, and her abilities also
increase, so please make effective use of it. However, please note
that the buff skill will be lost as Araka's corruption progresses.

Finally, in this game, except for the final boss, even if you are
defeated in battle, Araka will only suffer and weaken due to
corruption, but the game will still progress.
